ActAppropriation Act No. 2, 2005-2006
PrecisAppointment of YVES BRODEUR as Ambassador of Canada to Turkmenistan, with residence in Ankara; YVES BOULANGER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Djibouti, with residence in Addis Ababa; ROBERT McDOUGALL as Ambassador of Canada to the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia, with residence in Belgrade; CLAIRE A. POULIN as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Estonia, with residence in Riga; and PENNY REEDIE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Kingdom of Tonga, with concurrent accreditation to the Independent State of Samoa and to the Republic of Fiji, with residence in Wellington.
